  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Promoting Ethical Recruitment in the Hotel and Tourism Industry: Scaling Engagement and Enhancing Impact</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">This project aims to promote ethical recruitment and the IRIS programme in the hospitality and tourism Industry in a multi-faceted and multi-stakeholder manner. This project is built on a three-pillar strategy focused on private sector and employer engagement, private-public dialogue, and migrant-centred and civil society action. Building capacity, encouraging dialogue, and building cooperation towards upholding ethical recruitment are the core goals of this programme.</narrative>
  </description>
